{"word":"πειρατήριον","slug":"πειρατήριον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πειρατήριον</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:πεῖρα'><el>πεῖρα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><el>φόνια πειρατήρια</el> the murderous <i>ordeal</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a pirate's nest</i>, <b><a href='S:Strabo'>Strab.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>πειρᾱτής</el>\n"}]}